snippet.title: Echoes of the Fey: The Fox's Trail Release Trailer
snippet.description: Mystery and magic collide in Echoes of the Fey, a new visual novel series from Woodsy Studio beginning this summer with The Fox's Trail. A detective story set in a high fantasy world, The Fox's Trail follows Sofya Rykov, a private investigator with a magical secret who lives in works on the border between Humans and Leshin. For more information : http://woodsy-studio.com/echoes/
